column3: “A unique high tending towards clarity focus with a hint of Relaxation and it gets u hungry...  The uplift and euphoria are just amazing!”
“High is buzzy, euphoric and slightly psychedelic. The smell is amazing from both the sativa and the indica varieties. Worth a go. You get the munchies by the the third or fourth hit.”
“beautiful strain that grows naturally , good head high . expect some munchies.”
